Polokwane Municipality issued an alert about a power system emergency this morning (Wednesday) that Eskom may implement stage 1 and 2 load shedding between 09:00 and 23:00.
An announcement on Eskom’s website merely indicated that the situation is due to high demand or urgent maintenance being performed at certain power stations.
The load shedding schedule may be accessed on the municipality’s website https://www.polokwane.gov.za.